Mangalore Refinery Offers to Sell Fuel Oil for Loading in May

-- B y   Y e e   K a i   P i n
-- 
2011-03-25T00:47:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-25/mangalore-refinery-offers-to-sell-fuel-oil-for-loading-in-may.html
India’s  Mangalore Refinery &
Petrochemicals Ltd. (MRPL)  is offering to sell 80,000 metric tons of
 fuel oil  for May loading, the company said in a document e-
mailed to potential buyers.  Oil & Natural Gas Corp., the country’s biggest oil producer,
owns 72 percent of Mangalore Refinery.  Details of the offers are as follow:  To contact the reporter on this story:
